          "comment": "# 📰 Hacker News Agent\n\nAn agent scrapes the Hacker News front page, prioritizes posts matching your topic, and writes the digest straight to Markdown.\n\n**Pipeline:** Topic + instructions → HN agent (writes Markdown directly, no post-processing step) → output\n\n**Try this:** change the topic to steer coverage, or broaden it to cover the whole front page."
