      {
        "id": "4",
        "parent_id": null,
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "\nScrape the front page of https://news.ycombinator.com/ and write a themed Markdown digest.\n\nTopic focus: {{ topic }}\n- Prioritize front-page posts related to this topic.\n- If none match, cover the top general front-page posts instead and say so in the overview.\n\nTasks:\n1) Identify the top 5 relevant posts (topic matches first, then highest-ranked).\n2) For each post:\n   - Fetch the discussion thread with the browser tool.\n   - Extract the top 3 comments by score or prominence, with author and text.\n3) Write the final answer as Markdown with this structure:\n\n# Hacker News Digest: {{ topic }}\n\n<1-2 sentence overview of the themes across the selected posts>\n\n## <post title>\n<post url>\n\n**Top comments:**\n- **<author>:** <comment text>\n- **<author>:** <comment text>\n- **<author>:** <comment text>\n\n(repeat the \"## <post title>\" section once per post)\n"
        },
